{ "type": "Feature", "properties": { "id": 9901, "name": "大通闸", "direction": 120, "text":"大通闸始建于元至元二十九年(1292年)，元代郭守敬开凿通惠河，为控制水位落差而在沿线设置多处闸口，大通闸是其中之一。该闸是出元大都城向东的第一处闸口，初名“魏村闸”，百姓俗称“头闸”，地处东城与朝阳的交汇点，也是元大都东南护城河的拐角处，是通惠河上重要节点。20世纪60年代修建地铁时拆除，于闸口处改成暗河桥。现残存望水兽三件，安于此处后建桥梁之上。大通闸是大运河遗产的见证之一，成为研究北京漕运和城市发展的重要节点。", "auxiliary_storage_labeling_positionx": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_positiony": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_show": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_labelrotation": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_family": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_fontstyle": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_size": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_bold": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_italic": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_underline": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_color": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_strikeout": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_multilinealignment": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_buffersize": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_buffercolor": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_bufferdraw": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_labeldistance": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_hali": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_vali": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_scalevisibility": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_minscale": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_maxscale": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_alwaysshow": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_calloutdraw": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_labelallparts": null }, "geometry": { "type": "Point", "coordinates": [ 116.431406575754337, 39.901435905051997 ] } },
{ "type": "Feature", "properties": { "id": 9902, "name": "庆丰闸", "direction": 80, "img": [{"url":"/images/points/IMG_20250705_101739.jpg","caption":"庆丰闸遗址"}],"text":"庆丰闸始建于元至元二十九年（1292年），元代郭守敬开凿通惠河，为控制水位落差而在沿线设置多处闸口、庆丰闸是其中之一。该闸是出元大都城向东的第二处闸口，原名“籍东闸”，后改为“庆丰闸”，百姓俗称“二闸”。元、明、清三朝于河两岸存放加工大木，河南岸是“皇木厂”，自清乾隆年间改称“神木厂”，是因为在皇木厂内有京城五镇之“东方甲乙木”的镇位镇物，并有清乾隆帝御题神木谣碑一通。因河道拓宽，庆丰闸淹没水下。其遗址是大运河遗产的见证之一，成为研究北京漕运和城市发展的重要节点。\n（现场）","auxiliary_storage_labeling_positionx": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_positiony": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_show": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_labelrotation": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_family": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_fontstyle": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_size": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_bold": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_italic": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_underline": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_color": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_strikeout": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_multilinealignment": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_buffersize": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_buffercolor": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_bufferdraw": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_labeldistance": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_hali": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_vali": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_scalevisibility": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_minscale": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_maxscale": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_alwaysshow": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_calloutdraw": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_labelallparts": null }, "geometry": { "type": "Point", "coordinates": [ 116.462295983961681, 39.903079198732343 ] } },
